Interface PropertyWriter

All Known Implementing Classes:
ChemicalMarkupLanguage, MDLSD, PDF
public interface PropertyWriter

Interface for molecule file formats, which accepts descriptor values. For speed optimization of loading descriptor molecule files have a look at the ResultFactory.

Method Detail

write

boolean write(Molecule mol,
              String title,
              boolean writePairData,
              List attribs2write)
              throws IOException,
                     MoleculeIOException
Writes a molecule with his PairData.

Parameters:
mol - the molecule with additional data
title - the molecule title or null if the title from the molecule should be used
writePairData - if true then the additional molecule data is written
attrib2write - if null all PairData elements are written, otherwise all data elements are written which are listed in attrib2write.
Returns:
true if the molecule and the data has been succesfully written.
Throws:
IOException - Description of the Exception
MoleculeIOException
